  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of S18986 in the Treatment of Mild Cognitive Impairment Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of 15 mg and 50 mg of S18986 on Cognitive Symptoms in Mild Cognitive Impairment Patients Treated Over a 12-month Oral Administration Period</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Institut de Recherches Internationales Servier</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Servier</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate a long term efficacy of S18986 versus placebo on
      episodic memory performance in patients with MCI
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
